    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "The idol I pushed",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Welcome to Sapienza. \rWe client is a fanatic fan of cult graphic novel The Icon, who dissatisfied with the adaptation-or just say out, the subversion-of the novel by the film, so he want to assassinate Dino Bosco, the film&apos;s director and leading man. \rIn order to restore the original work, client asked to make it seem to be done by supernatural forces, which means don&apos;t disturb anyone, don&apos;t take anything, and let the target die overhead.\rThe clock is ticking, 47. Good luck.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as BlueberryMuffin.",
